. *************************************************
. *** DiD: Informality Decomposition **************
. **** Panels: Formal / Informal / Self-Emp *******
. **** Columns: All / NonInd-HLI / NonInd-Self ****
. ****          / Ind-HLI / Ind-Self **************
. *************************************************
. 
. foreach ds in year month {
  2. 
. do read-enigh`ds'.do
  3. estimates clear
  4. 
. *************************************************
. ************* Employment Categories *************
. *************************************************
. 
. if "`ds'" == "month" {
  5.     cap gen informal = (sar_afore1 != 1) if employed == 1
  6.     cap gen indep = indep1
  7. }
  8. 
. gen formal   = (informal == 0) if !missing(informal)
  9. gen self_emp = (indep == 1)    if !missing(indep)
 10. 
. *************************************************
. ****** Panel A: Formal Employment Outcome *******
. *************************************************
. 
. reghdfe formal i.zlfn##i.post $controls, absorb(ubica_geo year) vce(cluster u
> bica_geo)
